column5: You feeling better since the bees Lew?
You feeling better since the bees Lew?  Yup, 100% and thanks for asking.
Ya but Lew.  When do we get to see yours?  ?
Me too, never seen you simile, how big the Muskie, deer in the yard, bear in the yard, love tub chucked, Well, bees, nothing to smile about!  I have problem opening my chops too!
I can't and wouldn't disagree, always had a good time there and the people were great.
